        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Land business</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><persName>Mr. Hammeken</persName> wrote to me to buy him a horse&#8212; I have bought a mare
that will suit him, for one hundred dollars&#8212; I expect him dayly&#8212;keep
her untill he comes&#8212; I shall be down I expect <date when="1836-12-14">tomorrow </date>or <date when="1836-12-15">next day</date></p>

<p><persName>S. F. Austin</persName></p>

<p>I think I will go to <placeName>Brazoria </placeName>a while to arrange land business&#8212; I can
get no house here&#8212;</p>

<p>send me one hundred dollars to pay for the mare</p>
<p><persName>S. F. Austin</persName></p>

<p>Also send me two hundred dollars more making three hundred&#8212;</p>
<p><persName>S. F. Austin</persName></p>

<p>[Addressed:] <persName>Mr J. F. Perry</persName> <placeName>Peach point</placeName></p>

<p>[Endorsed by Perry:] <date when="1836-12-13">Decr 13th 1836</date></p>



        </div1>
